title: The Medieval Jousting Giraffe Weevil
description:
Good tidings, Wowzers! Where for art Mindy and Guy Raz this week, thou askth?! A renaissance fair! Join Mindy and Guy Raz in this ye ole episode of Wow in the World as they meet the a bug that jousts with its own nose! It's the what when, why, how and WOW of the Giraffe Weevil!
